ds-Pro-2-2023-USB-C',100,3.5,50,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/a/p/apple-airpods-pro-2-usb-c_8_.png',5),(25,'Sony','tai-nghe','Tai nghe khong day Sony WF-1000XM5 la su lua chon hoan hoa giup ban giai toa ap luc, cang thang sau gio lam viec hay cho ban dam chim vao nhung ban nhac ma minh yeu thich. Mang trong minh cong nghe chong on toi tan nhat thoi diem hien tai, tai nghe nhet tai nay cho ra chat luong am thanh chan thuc mot cach dang kinh ngac.',15,'Tai nghe Bluetooth True Wireless Sony WF-1000XM5',5590000,'Tai-nghe-Bluetooth-True-Wireless-Sony-WF-1000XM5',250,4.5,200,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/t/a/tai-nghe-khong-day-sony-wf-1000xm5-6_1.png',5),(26,'Apple','dien-thoai','iPhone 15 Pro Max 512GB la an pham smartphone moi cua Apple, noi bat voi bo nho trong len den 512GB, cung cap kha nang ghi nho, luu tru khong gioi han. Ben canh do, the he iPhone moi nay cung dac biet mang toi nhung trai nghiem sieu muot ma trong moi tac vu nho duoc ke thua suc manh xu ly tu con chip A17 Pro. Chua het, may con di kem voi cum ba camera sau 48MP ho tro chup dem va quay phim chuyen nghiep, giup nang tam kha nang nhiep anh cua nguoi dung.',0,'iPhone 15 Pro Max 512GB | Chinh hang VN/A',37490000,'iPhone-15-Pro-Max-512GB',100,4.5,200,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/i/p/iphone-15-pro-max_5.png',2),(27,'Samsung','dien-thoai','Samsung S24 Ultra la sieu pham smartphone dinh cao mo dau nam 2024 den tu nha Samsung voi chip Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 For Galaxy manh me, cong nghe tuong lai Galaxy AI cung khung vien Titan dang cap hua hen se mang toi nhieu su thay doi lon ve mat thiet ke va cau hinh. SS Galaxy S24 ban Ultra so huu man hinh 6.8 inch Dynamic AMOLED 2X tan so quet 120Hz. May cung so huu camera chinh 200MP, camera zoom quang hoc 50MP, camera tele 10MP va camera goc sieu rong 12MP.',20,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 12GB 256GB',26390000,'Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra-12GB-256GB',175,4,170,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/s/a/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra_9_.png',2),(28,'Apple','dong-ho-thong-minh','Apple Watch SE 2023 40mm (GPS) voi trang bi man hinh Retina cho hien thi vo cung sac net cung kinh cuong luc vo cung chac chan, sang trong va cuc ky dep mat. Kich thuoc dong ho la 44mm nho gon cung day deo cao su em ai. San pham Apple Watch SE 2023 duoc tich hop chip S8 SiP manh me, thoi gian su dung len den 18 gio.',25,'Apple Watch SE 2 2023 40mm (GPS) vien nhom | Chinh hang Apple Viet Nam',5890000,'Apple-Watch-SE-2-2023-40mm',50,5,125,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/2/a/2apple-watch-se-2023-40mm-vien-nhom-day-silicone-xanh-den-2.jpg',4),(29,'Samsung','dong-ho-thong-minh','Samsung watch 6 44mm chinh la su quan tam hang dau cua nhung nguoi dung yeu thich cac dong san pham dong ho thong minh hien nay. The he thu 6 da ke thua va cai tien rat tot phong cach thiet ke sang trong cung nhung tinh nang cao cap tu cac the he truoc. Chinh vi vay ma dong ho lan nay rat duoc ky vong se tiep tuc tro thanh mot sieu pham lam nuc long nguoi dung.',15,'Dong ho Samsung Galaxy Watch6 44mm',4390000,'Dong-ho-Samsung-Galaxy-Watch6-44mm',75,4.5,25,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/s/m/sm-r930_001_front_graphite_2.png',4),(30,'Asus','man-hinh','Man hinh Gaming ASUS TUF 24 VG249Q3A 24 inch so huu kich thuoc lon tren tam nen Fast IPS moi voi tan so quet len den 180Hz. Hon het man hinh Asus nay con co gam mau cuc chuan 99% sRGB, nen khong chi uu viet cho choi game ma con xu ly cong viec do hoa muot ma.',10,'Man hinh Gaming ASUS TUF VG249Q3A 24 inch',3490000,'Man-hinh-Gaming-ASUS-TUF-VG249Q3A-24-inch',15,4.5,50,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/m/a/man-hinh-gaming-asus-tuf-vg249q3a-24-inch_6_.png',7),(31,'Apple','may-tinh-bang','iPad mini. Thiet ke man hinh toan phan voi man hinh Liquid Retina 8.3 inch.1 Chip A15 Bionic manh me voi Neural Engine. Camera truoc Ultra Wide 12MP voi tinh nang Trung Tam Man Hinh. Cong ket noi USB-C. 5G sieu nhanh.2 Ghi chu, danh dau tai lieu hoac nam bat ngay khi nhung y tuong lon xuat hien trong dau voi Apple Pencil (the he thu 2). But gan ket bang nam cham va sac khong day.3\n\nTinh nang noi bat\nMan hinh Liquid Retina 8.3 inch tuyet dep voi True Tone va dai mau rong1\nChip A15 Bionic voi Neural Engine\nXac thuc bao mat voi Touch ID\nCamera sau Wide 12MP, camera truoc Ultra Wide 12MP voi tinh nang Trung Tam Man Hinh\nHien co mau Tim, Anh Sao, Hong va Xam Bac\nLoa stereo o canh tren va canh duoi\nMang 5G cho toc do tai xuong, xem video va nghe nhac truc tuyen nhanh nhu chop2\nLuon ket noi voi Wi-Fi 6 sieu nhanh\nThoi luong pin len toi 10 gio4\nCong ket noi USB-C de sac va ket noi phu kien\nTuong thich voi Apple Pencil (the he thu 2)3\niPadOS 15 so huu suc manh doc dao, de su dung va duoc thiet ke cho tinh da nang cua iPad.',0,'Apple iPad mini (6th Gen) Wi-Fi, 2021',11490000,'Apple-iPad-mini-(6th-Gen)-Wi-Fi-2021',402,4.7,170,'https://salt.tikicdn.com/cache/750x750/ts/product/49/75/99/2219ae33da6fb87ec3231dae0e752b3a.jpg.webp',3),(32,'Garmin','dong-ho-thong-minh','Dong ho Garmin Forerunner 165 la dong san pham duoc toi uu de ho tro viec luyen tap chuyen sau va cac van dong vien chuyen nghiep. Voi man hinh lon, do sang cao cung 5 phim bam vat ly, nguoi dung se luon co duoc kha nang dieu khien chinh xac, tien loi. Mau Garmin Forerunner chay bo cua Garmin con so huu thoi luong hoat dong len toi 11 ngay de su dung thoai mai trong nhieu ngay ma khong lo het pin.\n\nVi sao nen mua dong ho thong minh Garmin Forerunner 165?\nLa phien ban moi duoc ra mat, dong ho Forerunner 165 co nhung diem gi noi bat de xung dang tro thanh tro thu dac luc cho bo mon chay bo chuyen nghiep?\n\n- Thiet ke truyen thong kem man hinh lon: Garmin 165 so huu mat dong ho tron co do sang cao, kich thuoc lon toi 1,2 inch. Di kem la 5 phim bam vat ly de dam bao viec dieu khien luon dien ra chinh xac, tien loi\n\n- Toi uu cho viec luyen tap: Cac cam bien va chuong trinh luyen tap tren Garmin Forerunner 165 duoc thiet ke danh rieng cho nguoi chay bo va van dong vien\n\n- Dung luong pin lon: Dong ho thong minh moi  so huu vien pin co dung luong lon, du de thiet bi co the hoat dong lien tuc toi 11 ngay\n\n- Tich hop nhieu tinh nang tien loi: Dong ho con duoc tich hop san nhieu tinh nang tien loi nhu livetrack, phat canh bao khan cap, thong bao thong minh, thanh toan khong tiep xuc qua Garmin Pay,...\nGarmin Forerunner 165 - Tro thu dac luc cho mon chay bo chuyen nghiep\nDong ho thong minh Garmin Forerunner 165 duoc toi uu de danh rieng cho nhom doi tuong nguoi dung yeu thich chay bo va cac van dong vien chuyen nghiep. San pham duoc trang bi mot trong nhung mat dong ho co do sang cao nhat hien nay de luon dam bao duoc kha nang hien thi ro net. Dong thoi, dong ho con so huu thoi luong hoat dong an tuong de nguoi dung giam bot phien toai do phai sac pin lien tuc.\n\nThiet ke mat tron voi voi man hinh AMOLED kich thuoc lon, sac net\nDong ho Forerunner 165 duoc thiet ke voi mat dong ho tron truyen thong. Voi thiet ke nay, dong ho se phu hop de su dung voi moi do tuoi va gioi tinh. Xung quanh vien bezel, Garmin con trang bi toi 5 phim bam vat ly de ho tro nguoi dung dieu khien chinh xac hon trong qua trinh luyen tap.\nDiem nhan trong thiet ke cua Garmin 165 chinh la man hinh AMOLED co kich thuoc 1,2 inch giup mang toi khong gian hien thi thoai mai cho nguoi dung. Man hinh cua phien ban dong ho Forerunner 165 con co do sang cao de co the de dang su dung o moi truong ngoai nang. Di kem la kha nang khang nuoc chuan 5ATM de phu hop voi cac buoi tap cuong do cao khien nguoi dung do nhieu mo hoi.\n\nThoi luong hoat dong ben bi toi 11 ngay\nDong ho Garmin Forerunner 165 so huu cho minh mot vien pin co dung luong lon de co the hoat dong lien tuc toi 11 ngay. Con voi che do tiet kiem pin, dong ho 165 cua Garmin co the hoat dong toi da len den 20 ngay chi voi duy nhat mot lan sac. Dieu nay giup cho nguoi dung co the su dung dong ho cho viec luyen tap mot cach thoai mai trong thoi gian dai.\nNgay ca voi cac hoat dong the thao yeu cau thu thap du lieu thong qua GPS hay cac he thong dinh vi khac, dong ho Garmin Forerunner 165 van co the hoat dong trong khoang thoi gian tu 17 gio den 19 gio. Thoi gian nay du de nguoi dung co the su dung mau dong ho thong minh moi cua Garmin cho cac hoat dong the thao ngoai troi nhu di trekking, chay duong truong, di da ngoai.',0,'Dong ho thong minh Garmin Forerunner 165',6690000,'Dong-ho-thong-minh-Garmin-Forerunner-165',100,4.5,40,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/t/e/text_ng_n_-_2024-03-07t223511.209.png',4),(33,'Samsung','dong-ho-thong-minh','Samsung watch 6 44mm chinh la su quan tam hang dau cua nhung nguoi dung yeu thich cac dong san pham dong ho thong minh hien nay. The he thu 6 da ke thua va cai tien rat tot phong cach thiet ke sang trong cung nhung tinh nang cao cap tu cac the he truoc. Chinh vi vay ma dong ho lan nay rat duoc ky vong se tiep tuc tro thanh mot sieu pham lam nuc long nguoi dung.\n\nThiet ke dep mat, sang trong tao nen su noi bat\nSamsung Galaxy watch 6 44mm van duy tri duoc cho minh mot thiet ke voi ve ngoai day dang cap va thu hut tuong tu nhu nhung the he truoc. Mat dong ho Samsung duoc lam tu tinh the Sapphire mang tinh tham my, thanh lich cao. Dac biet o phien ban co dien cua dong sieu pham nay con trang bi khung vien nhom Armor Aluminum nang cao kha nang chong va dap hieu qua.\nChipset manh me, bo nho on dinh\nVoi nhung hua hen cho mot phien ban ke thua va cai tien day hoan hao. San pham Samsung Galaxy watch 6 lan nay se duoc mang mot bo khung ky thuat ma thong so cua no khien nhieu chiec dong ho thong minh khac phai ao uoc.\nDau tien phai ke den chinh la con chipset mang ten Exynos W930 SoC so huu suc manh lon gap nhieu lan so voi W920 tren cac dong cu truoc do. Va di kem con co la 2 GB Ram va 16 GB bo nho luu tru trong de toi uu hoa hieu qua cho trai nghiem cua nguoi su dung.\n\nKha nang ket noi va lam viec day hieu qua\nGalaxy watch 6 44mm den se duoc ho tro ket noi voi nhieu hinh thuc hon de giup tang su tien dung cho nguoi dung khi su dung. Mot so phuong thuc quen thuoc nhu  Wifi, Bluetooth, LTE se duoc ban de dang tim thay tren con sieu pham nay.\nNgoai ra cac tinh nang tu co ban den cao cap de giup ban duy tri va nang cao suc khoe van dong cua minh dua tren viec theo doi cac thong so do duoc tren chiec dong ho nay cung se duoc ho tro kem theo. Cac chi tieu SPO2, nhip tim, huyet ap, phan tich thanh phan co the, thoi luong ngu,… deu tich hop day du va chinh xac nhat.',0,'Dong ho Samsung Galaxy Watch6 44mm',4340000,'Dong-ho-Samsung-Galaxy-Watch6-44mm',200,4.2,70,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/s/m/sm-r930_001_front_graphite_2.png',4),(34,'Samsung','dong-ho-thong-minh','Dong ho Samsung Galaxy Fit 3 thiet ke thanh manh, gon gang, man hinh AMOLED 1.6 inch, trong luong chi 36.8g, khang nuoc 5ATM va bui IP68 cung vien pin 208mAh keo dai den 13 ngay an tuong tich hop sac khong day.\n\nVi sao nen mua dong ho Samsung Galaxy Fit 3?\nDong ho thong minh dang ngay cang duoc ua chuong va co nhieu ly do ma ban nen so huu mot chiec dong ho Galaxy Fit 3, cu the:\n\n- Thiet ke tre trung, nho gon tua mot chiec vong deo tay cung chat lieu cao cap va co chuan khang nuoc 5ATM, chong bui IP68;\n\n- Dong ho Samsung Fit 3 duoc trang bi vien pin nang cap voi thoi luong len den 13 ngay;\n\n- Dong ho con duoc trang bi cac cam bien tien tien voi kha nang do chi so chuan xac, theo doi nhip tim 24/7, theo doi giac ngu, cam bien SpO2,….;\n\n- Ho tro hon 100 che do luyen tap, giup nguoi dung nang cao suc khoe\nGalaxy Fit 3 – Thoi luong pin an tuong cho trai nghiem xuyen suot\nDong ho Samsung Galaxy Fit 3 la mau dong ho ke nhiem Galaxy Fit 2 so huu nhieu nang cap hua hen. Khong chi trang bi cam bien co do chuan xac tot hon, dong ho con duoc nang cap manh ve pin de cho ban yen tam su dung trong nhieu tuan lien.\n\nThiet ke gon nhe, tinh gian va kha nang khang nuoc 5ATM, khang bui IP68\nDong ho Galaxy Fit 3 co su thay doi ve mat thiet ke khi so huu mat dong ho dang chu nhat, man hinh  1.6 inch cung trong luong chi 36.8g. Voi thiet ke thanh manh, gon gang dong ho Galaxy Fit 3 cung chinh la mot mon phu kien hien dai.\nDong ho cung co vo nhom cao cap cung cac mau sac sang trong, thanh lich hon nhu Hong, Den, Bac,….Phan man hinh co kich thuoc lon hon Fit 2 tien nhiem voi man hinh AMOLED 1.6 inch, do phan giai 256x402 pixel, de giup ban de dang quan sat duoc nhieu thong tin tren thiet bi.\n\nCung voi do, thiet bi con co do khang nuoc 5ATM, khang bui IP68 nen ban cung co the su dung dong ho de di mua, boi loi,….\nTuy nhien, hang van khuyen nghi ban khong nen de dong ho tiep xuc truc tiep duoi nuoc nong, hoa chat, khong nen bam nut dieu khien khi dang o duoi nuoc,…de dam bao do ben.\n\nDong ho Galaxy Fit 3 so huu pin dai den 13 ngay\nMot diem duoc nang cap manh me tren dong ho Samsung Galaxy Fit 3 do chinh la thoi luong pin. Tren Fit 3, thoi luong pin keo dai den 13 ngay sau mot lan sac day voi vien pin 208mAh.\nVoi con so an tuong nay, Galaxy Fit 3 duoc danh gia la cho thoi luong pin tot hon so voi pin thong thuong cung phan khuc gia. Ben canh do, Fit 3 cung co toc do sac nhanh chong, sac day trong thoi gian ngan.\n\nCham soc suc khoe voi day du nhung cam bien, ket noi Bluetooth 5.3 on dinh\nTren dong ho Samsung Galaxy Fit 3, hang cung trang bi nhung cam bien hien dai va duoc nang cap de giup do dac cac chi so co the mot cach chuan xac hon. Cu the, dong ho co the do nhip tim 24/7 theo thoi gian thuc, theo doi giac ngu, do SpO2, theo doi chi so tap luyen the thao,….',0,'Dong ho Samsung Galaxy Fit 3',1390000,'Dong-ho-Samsung-Galaxy-Fit-3',300,5,210,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/s/a/samsung_3.png',4),(35,'JBL','loa','JBL Charge 5 – Sieu pham loa di dong the he moi, chat am vuot troi o moi khong gian\nTiep noi su thanh cong cua nguoi tien nhiem, dong loa huyen thoai loa JBL Charge 5 voi su thay doi manh me ca ve thiet ke lan cong nghe am thanh mang den chat luong am thanh vuot troi du la ngoai troi hay trong nha. La san pham loa bluetooth dong hanh cung ban o moi cuoc vui.\n\nThiet ke manh me, ho tro khang nuoc, chong bui tieu chuan IP67\nGiu nguyen phan thiet ke da lam nen thuong hieu dong Charge huyen thoai, JBL Charge 5 mang den ve be ngoai duoc trau chuot them tao them an tuong manh me cho nguoi dung khi lan dau tien nhin thay.\nCu loa thiet ke moi mang den chat luong am thanh to va ro rang\nCharge 5 su dung cu loa moi voi ten goi “Racetrack-shaped driver” tang tiet dien loa, giup the hien am sac voi bien do rong hon.\nCung voi do la 2 loa tweeter va mang rung thu dong JBL Bass Radiators giup tang cuong am bass voi do sau tot hon, dai cao duoc cai thien sang ro hon so voi nguoi tien nhiem.\n\nDung luong pin len den 7500mAh, ho tro sac cho cac thiet bi di dong\nMang den cho nguoi dung kha nang giai tri bat tan voi hon 20 gio su dung nho vien pin 7500mAh ben trong loa bluetooth JBL Charge 5. Ngoai ra thong qua cong USB duoc tich hop san, ban co the su dung loa nhu mot vien pin du phong de cung cap them nang luong cho cac chiec smartphone cua minh.\nTiec vui them ron ra voi cong nghe PartyBoost ket noi khong gioi han voi cac loa khac\nCong nghe PartyBoost doc quyen tu JBL giup ban ghep hai hay nhieu loa co ho tro cong nghe nay voi nhau de tang them cong suat phat, tu do giup bua tiec cua ban cang them soi dong.\nJBL Charge 5 tich hop cong nghe ket noi khong day Bluetooth 5.1 giup ket noi nhanh va on dinh, truyen tai am thanh khong day voi chat luong tot cho nguoi nghe.',0,'Loa Bluetooth JBL Charge 51',3790000,'Loa-Bluetooth-JBL-Charge-5',26,4.8,11,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:358:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/g/r/group_211.png',10),(36,'Garmin','dong-ho-thong-minh','Dong ho thong minh Garmin Forerunner 55 – Em ut nha Garmin\nBan da qua quen thuoc voi cac thiet bi dong ho deo tay cao cap dat tien cua Garmin, nhung lan nay con gi tuyet hon khi ban duoc trai nghiem toan bo tinh nang hap dan tren chiec dong ho thong minh Garmin Forerunner 55 voi so huu muc gia chi roi vao tu 200 do.\n\nThiet ke tinh gian hon, nang cap ve phan mem\nNham giup nguoi dung tro nen thanh lich hon voi mau ma khong con qua ham ho nhu xua, dong ho thong minh Garmin Forerunner 55 duoc got bot phan than vo sao cho goc canh hon, trong noi bat hon voi kieu dang cung cap va bat mat hon. Nguoi dung co the tinh chinh bang cach thao lap day ra va doi moi ve ngoai neu ban cam thay chan.\nTich hop nhung tinh nang noi bat\nNham giup dap ung day du va tang cuong trai nghiem nguoi dung, dong ho thong minh Garmin so huu nhieu tinh nang tu co ban den nang cao bao gom: tinh nang goi y bai tap the thao moi ngay, tinh nang chay vong lap ho tro cho cac van dong vien nham do dac thong so chinh xac hon va do buoc chay trong thoi gian thuc.\nNgoai ra, chiec dong ho thong minh gia re den tu Garmin con duoc trang bi them tinh nang ho tro cho nguoi tap luyen va cu the la nguoi di bo voi lich trinh do quang duong da duoc thiet lap tu truoc. Ben canh do, no con duoc nang cap them thoi luong pin voi thoi gian su dung voi 20 gio khi su dung tinh nang GPS va 14 ngay voi thiet lap binh thuong.',0,'Dong ho thong minh Garmin Forerunner 55',5020000,'Dong-ho-thong-minh-Garmin-Forerunner-55',120,4.7,17,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/d/o/dong-ho-thong-minh-garmin-forerunner-55-1.jpg',4),(37,'Garmin','dong-ho-thong-minh','La chiec dong ho duoc thiet ke theo phong cach the thao. Do do, Garmin Forerunner 965 cuc ky chu trong vao viec tich hop nhieu che do luyen tap da dang va vien pin voi dung luong “trau” de moi nguoi su dung thoai mai hon. Man hinh kich thuoc 1.4 inch cung tam nen AMOLED mang den nheu khong gian hien thi va hinh anh ruc ro, sac net. Cung CellphoneS tim hieu them ve chiec dong ho Garmin vua moi ra mat nay nhe.\n\nDong ho Garmin Forerunner 965 - Pin “trau”, che do luyen tap da dang\nMan hinh AMOLED sac net\nVoi kieu dang mat dong ho tron, Forerunner 965 so huu kich thuoc lon dat 1.4 inch xung quanh duoc bao boc boi mot khung bezel titan moi. Dieu do da gop phan giup dong ho co duoc khong gian hien thi mo rong, nguoi dung co the xem duoc nhieu thong bao hon ma khong can phai cuon luot lien tuc. \nDi kem voi do la trang bi tam nen AMOLED co do phan giai 454 x 454 px. Tu do, thiet bi co kha nang hien thi mau sac chan thuc va co phan ruc ro hon. Dac biet, tam nen AMOLED con ho tro chong choi nen co the quan sat tot ngay khi dung duoi anh nang mat troi. \n\nDung luong pin len den 23 ngay, man hinh cam ung va nut bam sieu nhay\nVoi vien pin lon, dong ho Garmin 965 duoc nang len thoi gian trai nghiem den 31 gio khi dung o che do chi GPS khong co nhac. Thoi luong do con co the keo dai lien tuc 23 ngay khi dung o che do dong ho thong minh. Do do, ban co the tu tin su dung khi di du lich hoac da ngoai ma khong can lo lang bi gian doan.\nNgoai kha nang hien thi sac net tren be mat rong hon thi dong ho Garmin Forerunner 965 con tich hop tinh nang cam ung cho man hinh, giup ban de dang thao tac. Ben canh do, thiet bi cung trang bi 5 nut cung vat ly sieu nhay, ho tro ban dieu khien trong khi tay uot hoac ra mo hoi khien cam ung khong dung duoc.\n\nHon nua, mat dong ho con duoc bao ve ben bi boi lop kinh cuong luc Corning Gorilla 3 DX. Do do, dong ho duoc bao ve lau dai hon, chong xuoc va giam thieu cac tac dong do ngoai luc tu ben ngoai.\n\nXay dung ke hoach tap luyen voi cac tinh nang vuot troi\nKhong chi dem den thoi luong pin “khoe” ma dong ho Forerunner 965 con cung cap den ban mot ke hoach tap luyen voi nhieu bai tap da dang.  Trong do, thiet bi se ho tro tap luyen tim mach, tap luyen suc manh, tap luyen HIIT (giam mo toan than), tap Yoga, tap luyen Pilates,...cung nhieu mon the thao khac nhau, de ban ren luyen suc khoe moi ngay.\nDi kem ho tro cho cac che do tap luyen la cac tinh nang theo doi suc khoe thong minh vuot troi duoc Garmin Forerunner 965 trang bi hang loat. Dien hinh nhu do dien tim tam do, do do bao hoa oxy trong mau, dem so buoc di va phat hien som cac chi so bat thuong hay theo doi chu ky kinh nguyet.\nBan do tich hop voi GPS Multiband va SatIQ\nHuong den nguoi dung dam me the thao, dong ho Garmin Forerunner 965 da tich hop ban do voi cong nghe SatIQ, voi day mau sac de giup ban di dung huong, chinh phuc duoc moi cung duong o bat ky dau tren map ma khong can lo lang bi lac.\nDong thoi, thiet bi cung se co them tinh nang phat hien su co di kem de ho tro gui vi tri den cac so dien thoai thiet lap san, nen ban co the yen tam kham pha.\nThiet ke Garmin Forerunner 965 nang dong cung vien titan an tuong\nThiet ke cua Garmin Forerunner 965 mang ve nang dong nhung vo cung manh me. Cung voi do la phan day deo bang silicon mem deo, tao do thoai mai, thoang khi de thoai mai deo ca ngay dai ma khong lo bi nong bi. \nKhung vien cua dong ho duoc lam bang chat lieu titan ben bi, khong lo gi set an tuong. Thiet bi se con cung cap den nguoi dung 3 su chon lua mau sac la den, trang va vang. Dong thoi, san pham con duoc trang bi chuan chong nuoc 5ATM. Do do, ban co the deo Garmin 965 khi rua tay hoac di mua nhe ma van an toan cho thiet bi.',0,'Dong ho thong minh Garmin Forerunner 965',15660000,'Dong-ho-thong-minh-Garmin-Forerunner-965',202,4.9,121,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/g/a/garmin-forerunner-965-den-1.jpg',4),(38,'ViewSonic','man-hinh','Man hinh ViewSonic VA2209-H 100Hz 22 inch - Chat luong hinh anh dep, toi uu cho nhieu muc dich\nMan hinh ViewSonic VA2209-H 100Hz 22 inch giup ban tan huong mau sac phong phu voi do sang on dinh den tu moi goc nhin. Voi nhieu cong nghe ho tro tien tien khac, mau man hinh ViewSonic se co muc tieu thu dien nang thap de ban thoai mai su dung cho nhieu nhu cau khac nhau.\n\nHien thi Full HD sac net o moi goc nhin, tan so quet 100Hz\nMan hinh ViewSonic VA2209-H 100Hz 22 inch so huu do phan giai Full HD 1080p. Dieu nay ket hop cung cong nghe SuperClear IPS se giup ban trai nghiem duoc khung hinh hien thi ro net va do chi tiet dang kinh ngac voi goc nhin rong toi 178 do.\nVoi toc do lam moi 100Hz, man hinh con cho ra nhung chuyen dong hinh anh muot ma, lien mach tuyet voi ngay ca o cac hanh dong nhanh. Them vao do, man hinh con duoc ViewSonic cung cap hang loat cac cai dat theo tung noi dung nhu Game/Movie//Text/Web,... voi do tuong phan va do sang toi uu theo nhieu muc dich.\n\nThiet ke 3 canh khong vien, giam hien tuong xe hinh\nMan hinh ViewSonic VA2209-H 100Hz 22 inch duoc lam voi thiet ke 3 canh khong vien, ho tro thiet lap nhieu man hinh mot cach lien mach. Ket hop voi do la cong nghe Flicker Free / Blue Light Filter loc anh sang xanh, han che moi mat.\nBen canh do, ViewSonic con tich hop them cong nghe Adaptive Sync de giam thieu hien tuong xe hinh. Tu do, o toc do khung hinh nhanh thi noi dung van duoc hien thi, chuyen dong muot va han che mo nhoe.',0,'Man hinh ViewSonic VA2209-H 100Hz 22 inch',1890000,'Man-hinh-ViewSonic-VA2209-H-100Hz-22-inch',202,3.7,12,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/m/a/man-hinh-viewsonic-va2209-h-100hz-22-inch.png',7),(39,'Samsung','may-tinh-bang','DAC DIEM NOI BAT\nGalaxy AI tien ich - Ho tro dich, tom tat van ban, chinh sua anh thong minh va dich am thanh\nSong dong va sac net moi khung hinh - Man hinh 14.6 inch Dynamic AMOLED 2X,Tan so quet den 120Hz cung HDR10+\nXu li muot ma ke ca tac vu nang voi chip xu li Snapdragon® 8 Gen 2 for Galaxy manh me\nBen bi cho moi hanh trinh suon se - Khang bui va nuoc dat chuan IP68 cung chat lieu nhom Armor Aluminum giup han che cong va xuoc\nSang tao moi luc moi noi - But S Pen moi voi do tre cuc thap chi 2.8ms, ho tro nhieu ung dung chuyen dung: Goodnotes5, LumaFusion',11,'Samsung Galaxy Tab S9 Ultra 12GB 512GB',23190000,'Samsung-Galaxy-Tab-S9-Ultra-12GB-512GB',55,3.9,38,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/s/s/ss-tab-s9-ultra_1__1.png',3),(40,'Sony','loa','Loa Sony SRS-XE200 - Thiet ke nho gon, am thanh vuot troi\nLoa bluetooth Sony SRX-XE200 nam trong bo suu tap moi nhat cua X-series voi thiet ke va tinh nang cai tien. Kieu dang thiet bi gon nhe nen ban co the mang den bat cu dau de tan huong am nhac.\n\nBo khuech dai dang duong thang cho am thanh truyen xa hon\nBo khuech tan duong thang cua Sony SRS-XE200 giup phan phoi va truyen am thanh di xa hon tren pham vi rong ma khong bi anh huong den chat luong. Thiet ke nay duoc lay cam hung tu cac buoi hoa nhac lon cho khong gian tran ngap cac giai dieu. Nhu vay, ban se cam nhan duoc cung mot chat luong am thanh ke ca o phia truoc hay ben canh loa.\nKich thuoc nho gon, day deo tien dung\nSan pham so huu thiet ke nho gon, co them day deo giup cho viec mang theo ben nguoi cang them de dang. Voi trong luong chua den 1kg nen loa Sony SRS-XE200 rat tien cho viec mang den cac bua tiec hoac cac chuyen di phuot. Vo loa Sony duoc lam bang chat lieu rat ben bi, co the dat dung hoac nam tuy theo nguoi dung.\nX-Balanced Speaker Unit moi co mang loa khong tron, cho am thanh chat luong cao\nKhac so voi mang loa tron truyen thong, Sony SRS-XE200 so huu man loa khong tron ho tro tao ap suat am thanh cao, mang den trai nghiem tuyet voi hon, dong thoi han che bien dang am thanh. Them vao do, thiet ke cac loa lech tam nhau ket hop do can bang trong luong tang chi tiet am thanh va mo rong am tang. Ngoai ra, san pham con so huu bo tan am thu dong kep nham tao ra cac am tram manh me.\nPin len den 16 gio su dung va tich hop cam bien chong tieng on xung quanh\nLoa bluetooth SRS-XE200 duoc nha san xuat uu ai cho luong pin khung co the len den 16h, du de phuc vu moi cuoc vui choi. Cung voi cong nghe cam bien mic doc dao cua Sony, Ambient Noise Sensing giup tiet kiem pin khi su dung ben ngoai.\n\nNeu cam thay minh khong du thoi gian sac, thi ban co the sac loa 10 phut de doi loai 70 phut choi. Ben canh do, loa con co tinh nang cham soc pin nen ban khong phai lo lang ve tuoi tho cua pin.\nChong nuoc, chong bui vuot troi dat chuan IP67\nSony SRS-XE200 duoc trang bi kha nang chong nuoc chong bui va chong tham nuoc chuan IP67. Do do, ban co the yen tam khi mang loa di bien, den ho boi, cong vien hoac san vuon. Ngoai ra, thiet bi con duoc trang bi them kha nang chong soc MIL STD 810 H o do cao 1.22m, giup han che kha nang hu hong khi lo tay lam roi loa.\nCuoc goi cai thien voi Echo Cancelling\nHai nguoi co the cung noi chuyen ma khong bi gian doan. Ben canh do, ban co the tat tieng ngay lap tuc bang nut “MIC Mute” ngay tren loa mot cach de dang. Va voi tinh nang ket noi da diem, co the ket noi cung luc hai thiet bi.',0,'Loa Bluetooth Sony SRS-XE200',1150000,'Loa-Bluetooth-Sony-SRS-XE200',125,3.6,88,'https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/insecure/rs:fill:0:358/q:90/plain/https://cellphones.com.vn/media/catalog/product/_/0/_0003_srs-xe200_4_.jpg',10),(47,'Chuot','Chuot-may-tinh','a',20,'a',20000,'a',20,0,0,'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/lavenshop-c9862.appspot.com/o/product_images%2F1729091287683.jpeg?alt=media&token=628cae9f-c263-4bde-8640-1b6a9490bd32',6);
